| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3915 — Recovery Inhibition (8base)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9fe4bb6c-3128-5d9c-83ef-f45c8dd1fda8"
